name: real
description: $REAL is a pure memecoin born from culture, not utility. It isn’t about complex roadmaps or tech promises—it’s about community, narrative, and identity. The Word “Real” is already part of internet and Gen Z culture. On TikTok, #real has over 45M+ posts, and on X, people use “real” every day to agree or show conviction. The Movement: Being $REAL means being authentic in a market full of fakes. It’s about community members working together and pushing a shared vision. The Narrative: The value of $REAL comes from its cultural weight. Everyone already says it, everyone already relates to it—now the meme has a token to live through.
